main event: Six luminous objects were observed in Nashville, Tennessee on July 23, 1965.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for about 3-4 minutes,The objects appeared to change to an aircraft configuration mid-flight,The observation was conducted visually at night with a clear view,The objects were confirmed to be in an area where an USAF T-33 jet fighter was located,No physical evidence or photographs were recorded.
sighted object: six luminous objects in the sky
witness description: The observer reported a visual sighting while driving.
